    "readme": "\u003ch1\u003e\n\u003ca id=\"user-content-spincer-shared-performance-monitoring-and-analysis-microservice\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#spincer-shared-performance-monitoring-and-analysis-microservice\" aria-hidden=\"true\"\u003e\u003cspan aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003eSPINCER: Shared Performance monItoring and aNalysis miCrosERvice\u003c/h1\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis is an experimental repo containing a performance monitoring and analysis microservice\nfor the TAU performance system. SPINCER is designed using the Mochi software stack.\u003c/p\u003e\n",
